-- Rogers of Mauritius's Annual Profit to Fall 40%, Week-end Says, Citing CEO
-- Kamlesh Bhuckory
-- 2010-08-02T06:08:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-02/rogers-of-mauritius-s-annual-profit-to-fall-40-week-end-says-citing-ceo.html

          
          
             Rogers & Co. Ltd. , a Mauritian
company with interests in tourism and financial services,
expects profit to fall as much as 40 percent this year from a
year earlier,  Week-end reported , citing an interview with
General Manager Philippe Espitalier-Noel.  
